		<div class="comment snook" id="c60435">
		<div class="meta">
			<div class="commentnumber"><a href="#c60435">6</a></div>
			<span class="authorname">Jonathan Snook</span> said on December 02, 2008		</div>
		<div class="quote"><p>@Dan: I wanted a custom platform because of the ability to simplify the process and have the system as straightforward to use and manage for advertisers and administrators alike. We don't have multiple ad types, we don't charge based on impressions or clickthroughs. It's a simple, monthly, flat-fee system. As a result, we wanted something that served that goal. The original system (which is still running SidebarAds) was put together over a couple days. It's only now, as we expand, that there's more of a demand to expand those features, but again in ways that serve the goal of simplicity.
</p>
</div>
